c Stokes drag\nforce, while the aerodynamic drag force is a predominant factor for the\npropagation of ICME with V - V_bg > 2300 km/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2014 15:22:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-08"}
